<body id="body" class="bg-white text-gray-900">
{{> header_amp}}

<main class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-12">

	<ul class="broadcrumbs mt-15" vocab="https://schema.org/" typeof="BreadcrumbList">
			<li property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem">
				<a property="item" typeof="Thing" href="/" class="hover:underline">
					<span property="name">Stakers.space</span>
				</a>
				<meta property="position" content="1">
			</li>
			<li property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem">
				<a property="item" typeof="Thing" href="/pricing" class="hover:underline">
					<span property="name">Pricing</span>
				</a>
				<meta property="position" content="2">
			</li>
		</ul>
  <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-10">Pricing</h1>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Stakers.space is an 
    <a href="https://github.com/Stakers-space/Web" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-700 hover:underline">open-source</a> 
    platform designed to provide valuable guides, tools, and information on staking — 
    the process of securing networks that run on public ledgers protected by the Proof of Stake (PoS) mechanism.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">Stakers.space Website</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    <strong class="font-semibold">Access to and use of the website’s content is completely free.</strong> 
    Open-source resources can be used at no cost for personal purposes.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">Stakers.space Account / Dashboard</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    For personalized guides and access to additional tools, 
    <strong class="font-semibold">a Stakers.space account offers free trial for the period of the first 30 days</strong> 
    and then is available under a fee starting at 
    <strong class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">$129 per year</strong>.
    The subscription unlocks tailored instructions, validator monitoring, alerts and exclusive features. 
    It applies to <strong>manager accounts only (node operators)</strong>; 
    <span class="italic">client-based accounts are always free</span>.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">Stakers.space API</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    The Stakers.space API is available on a credit-based system. 
    Credits are consumed based on interactions with the Stakers.space server, 
    offering flexible and scalable access to the platform’s resources.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">Liquid staking through Stakers.space Vaults</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    Fees for using Stakers.space-operated vaults are listed in each individual vault’s prospect.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">
    Using 
    <a href="/ethereum-staking/smoothing-pool" class="text-emerald-700 hover:underline">Smoothing Pool</a>
  </h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    Fees for using the Stakers.space smoothing pool will be provided on the Smoothing Pool presentation page.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-16 mb-4">Tailored Tools Development</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    We offer development of various tools around staking. 
    Pricing is calculated based on the project scope and technical specification.
    For more details, contact us at 
    <a href="mailto:stakersspace@proton.me" class="text-emerald-700 hover:underline">stakersspace@proton.me</a>.
  </p>

</main>

